appoint an official from the U.S. Information Agency to be
stationed at the Swiss embassy, which has been taking care of
American interests in Iran.
</P>
<P>
Kharrazi said that as long as the U.S. does not change its
hostile policy, Iran will not "waste time with it".
</P>
<P>
