strengthen the time-tested friendship with China, Minister of
State for Foreign Affairs Muhammad Siddique Khan said here
Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
While meeting a five-member delegation of the Chinese People
Association for Friendship with Foreign Countries (CPAFFC),
Siddique Khan highly praised the Pak-China relations.
</P>
