Kashmir and on Pakistan's efforts to bring about a peaceful
solution to the conflict in Afghanistan.
</P>
<P>
Vice Chairman of the CPAFFC and leader of the Chinese
delegation Su Guang said that China also hopes to further boost
ties between the two countries.
</P>
<P>
Su briefed the host on the history and current situation of the
CPAFFC.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese delegation arrived here Monday evening on a
five-day visit to Pakistan at the invitation of the All
Pakistan-China Friendship Association. 
