<HEADLINE> Chinese Vice-Premier Talks with UN Secretary-General (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Qian said that the Chinese government has always been concerned
about the situation in the Middle East and supports a more
positive role in the Middle East for the UN and the
Secretary-general.
</P>
<P>
Qian said that security and peace are inseparable and that
