three of the F5 Canadian fighter bombers purchased by the BDF
last year.
</P>
<P>
Details have not been released but it has been reported widely
that the BDF purchased 12 of the aircraft.
</P>
<P>
At the conclusion of the flypast, Jamieson presented Khama
with the keys of U.S.-manufactured airboats the BDF will use in
its anti-poaching operations on Botswana's northern border.
