<HEADLINE> Air Service Connects Northeast China's Harbin to Seoul </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HARBIN, March 31 (Xinhua) -- Regular direct air service began
today connecting Harbin, capital of northeast China's Heilongjiang
Province, and Seoul of the Republic of Korea (ROK).
</P>
<P>
