flight time is three hours. There will be four flights a week.
</P>
<P>
China Northern Airlines and an air company of the ROK will
jointly operate the service. MD-82 and Boeing aircrafts will be
used, according to China Northern Airlines, which is based in
Shenyang, capital of northeast China's Liaoning Province.
